[{"id": 129755, "identifier": "cs.nykl", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 558, "ruku": 492, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "cs", "name": "Nykl", "transelator_en_name": "A. R. Nykl", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5218, "text": "\u00d3 proroku! - Zapuzujete-li \u017eeny sv\u00e9, tedy zapuzujte je dle obdob\u00ed jejich, a po\u010d\u00edtejte obdob\u00ed ta p\u0159esn\u011b: a bojte se Boha, P\u00e1na sv\u00e9ho. Nevyh\u00e1n\u011bjte jich z dom\u016f jejich a nevyh\u00e1n\u011bjte jich, leda\u017ee by dopou\u0161t\u011bly se cizolo\u017estv\u00ed zjevn\u00e9ho. Tyto jsou hranice (na\u0159\u00edzen\u00ed) bo\u017e\u00edho a kdo p\u0159estupuje hranice bo\u017e\u00ed, k\u0159ivd\u00ed sob\u011b sam\u00e9mu: nev\u00ed\u0161 p\u0159ece, zda snad B\u016fh vzbud\u00ed pot\u00e9 okolnost n\u011bjakou."}, {"id": 129757, "identifier": "cs.nykl", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 558, "ruku": 492, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "cs", "name": "Nykl", "transelator_en_name": "A. R. Nykl", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5219, "text": "A kdy\u017e dos\u00e1hly ur\u010den\u00e9 lh\u016fty sv\u00e9, bu\u010f vezm\u011bte je zp\u011bt laskav\u011b, aneb rozejd\u011bte se s nimi laskav\u011b: a p\u0159ive\u010fte za sv\u011bdky osoby spravedliv\u00e9 z va\u0161eho st\u0159edu a sv\u011bdectv\u00ed (p\u0159\u00edm\u00e9) \u010di\u0148te p\u0159ed Bohem. T\u00edmto napom\u00edn\u00e1n jest, kdo\u017ekoliv v\u011b\u0159\u00ed v Boha a v den posledn\u00ed: a kdo\u017ekoliv boj\u00ed se Boha, tomu pop\u0159eje B\u016fh (dobr\u00e9ho) v\u00fdsledku!"}, {"id": 129758, "identifier": "cs.nykl", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 558, "ruku": 492, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "cs", "name": "Nykl", "transelator_en_name": "A. R. Nykl", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5220, "text": "a obda\u0159\u00ed jej, zkad (odkud ) nenad\u011bje se. A tomu, kdo spol\u00e9h\u00e1 na Boha, sta\u010d\u00ed B\u016fh; B\u016fh zajist\u00e9 dos\u00e1hne c\u00edl\u016f sv\u00fdch: dalt\u011b B\u016fh v\u0161em v\u011bcem p\u0159edur\u010den\u00ed."}, {"id": 129759, "identifier": "cs.nykl", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 558, "ruku": 492, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "cs", "name": "Nykl", "transelator_en_name": "A. R. Nykl", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5221, "text": "Pokud se t\u00fd\u010de on\u011bch \u017een va\u0161ich, je\u017e nemaj\u00ed nad\u011bje na \u010dm\u00fdru (menstruaci) - m\u00e1te-li pochybnosti o tom - tehdy obdob\u00ed jejich budi\u017e t\u0159i m\u011bs\u00edce, a stejn\u011b takov\u00e9 pro ty, je\u017e dosud nem\u011bly \u010dm\u00fdry: a pro ty, je\u017e t\u011bhotn\u00e9 jsou, lh\u016fta bude dokud neslehly. A tomu, kdo boj\u00ed se Boha, B\u016fh usnadn\u00ed z\u00e1le\u017eitost jeho."}, {"id": 129760, "identifier": "cs.nykl", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 558, "ruku": 492, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "cs", "name": "Nykl", "transelator_en_name": "A. R. Nykl", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5222, "text": "Takov\u00fdto jest rozkaz bo\u017e\u00ed, jej\u017e seslal v\u00e1m a tomu, jen\u017e boj\u00ed se Boha, B\u016fh odejme \u0161patnosti jeho a zv\u011bt\u0161\u00ed mu odm\u011bnu."}, {"id": 129761, "identifier": "cs.nykl", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 559, "ruku": 492, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "cs", "name": "Nykl", "transelator_en_name": "A. R. Nykl", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5223, "text": "Dejte p\u0159\u00edbytek (zapuzen\u00fdm) tam, kde sami bydl\u00edte, dle prost\u0159edk\u016f sv\u00fdch; a ne\u010di\u0148te jim p\u0159\u00edko\u0159\u00ed, tak abyste vh\u00e1n\u011bli je v t\u00edse\u0148: a jsou-li t\u011bhotny, tedy d\u00e1vejte na n\u011b, dokud neslehnou; a kdy\u017e koj\u00ed v\u00e1m (d\u011bcko), d\u00e1vejte jim plat jejich a pora\u010fte se mezi sebou v laskavosti; v\u0161ak naleznete-li v tom n\u011bjak\u00fdch obt\u00ed\u017e\u00ed, te\u010f nech\u0165 koj\u00ed (d\u011bcko) \u017eena jin\u00e1."}, {"id": 129762, "identifier": "cs.nykl", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 559, "ruku": 492, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "cs", "name": "Nykl", "transelator_en_name": "A. R. Nykl", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5224, "text": "Ten pak, kdo z\u00e1mo\u017en\u00fd jest, nech\u0165 d\u00e1v\u00e1 dle z\u00e1mo\u017enosti sv\u00e9: a ten, jeho\u017e \u017eivobyt\u00ed odm\u011b\u0159eno jest, nech\u0165 d\u00e1v\u00e1 dle toho, co dal mu B\u016fh. B\u016fh neukl\u00e1d\u00e1 du\u0161i v\u011bt\u0161\u00edho b\u0159emena. ne\u017e dle toho, co byl dal j\u00ed: a B\u016fh po t\u011b\u017ekostech uleh\u010d\u00ed."}, {"id": 129763, "identifier": "cs.nykl", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 559, "ruku": 493, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "cs", "name": "Nykl", "transelator_en_name": "A. R. Nykl", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5225, "text": "A kolik m\u011bst odvr\u00e1tilo se od rozkazu P\u00e1na sv\u00e9ho a prorok\u016f jeho! A s\u00fa\u010dtovali jsme s nimi s\u00fa\u010dtov\u00e1n\u00edm p\u0159\u00edsn\u00fdm a ztrestali jsme je trestem odporn\u00fdm."}, {"id": 129764, "identifier": "cs.nykl", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 559, "ruku": 493, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "cs", "name": "Nykl", "transelator_en_name": "A. R. Nykl", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5226, "text": "A okusila b\u011bdnost postaven\u00ed sv\u00e9ho a konec postaven\u00ed jejich byla z\u00e1huba (pln\u00e1)."}, {"id": 129765, "identifier": "cs.nykl", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 559, "ruku": 493, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "cs", "name": "Nykl", "transelator_en_name": "A. R. Nykl", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5227, "text": "Schystal jim B\u016fh trest p\u0159\u00edsn\u00fd: pro\u010de\u017e bojte se Boha, lid\u00e9 (pronikav\u00e9ho) rozumu, kdo\u017e uv\u011b\u0159ili jste, neb B\u016fh seslal v\u00e1m ji\u017e napomenut\u00ed:"}, {"id": 129766, "identifier": "cs.nykl", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 559, "ruku": 493, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "cs", "name": "Nykl", "transelator_en_name": "A. R. Nykl", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5228, "text": "proroka, jen\u017e p\u0159ed\u010d\u00edt\u00e1 v\u00e1m znamen\u00ed bo\u017e\u00ed jasn\u00e1, aby vyvedl ty, kdo\u017e uv\u011b\u0159ili a konaj\u00ed dobr\u00e9 skutky, z temnot na sv\u011btlo; a toho, jen\u017e v\u011b\u0159\u00ed v Boha a kon\u00e1 dobro, uvede (B\u016fh) v zahrady, pod nimi\u017e \u0159eky tekou - v nich p\u0159eb\u00fdvati budou v\u011b\u010dn\u011b v\u011bk\u016fv a p\u0159ekr\u00e1sn\u00e9 pro\u0148, B\u016fh schystal \u017eivobyt\u00ed!"}, {"id": 129767, "identifier": "cs.nykl", "surah_number": 65, "surah_ar_name": "\u0633\u0648\u0631\u0629 \u0627\u0644\u0637\u0644\u0627\u0642", "surah_en_name": "At-Talaaq", "surah_en_name_translation": "Divorce", "revelation_type": "Medinan", "juz": 28, "manzil": 7, "page": 559, "ruku": 493, "hizb_quarter": 223, "sajda": false, "sajda_id": 0, "sajda_obligatory": false, "sajda_recommended": false, "language": "cs", "name": "Nykl", "transelator_en_name": "A. R. Nykl", "format": "text", "type": "translation", "ayah_number": 5229, "text": "B\u016fh jest to, jen\u017e stvo\u0159il sedmero nebes a zem\u00ed tolik\u00e9\u017e: rozkaz (jeho) sestupuje mezi nimi, aby v\u011bd\u011bli jste, \u017ee B\u016fh zajist\u00e9 nade v\u0161emi v\u011bcmi moc m\u00e1 a \u017ee B\u016fh zajist\u00e9 v\u0161echny v\u011bci obklopuje v\u011bd\u011bn\u00edm sv\u00fdm."}]